      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been meticulously preserved to ensure an experience indistinguishable from new. We invite you to acquire a truly impeccable example of engineering excellence.",
