    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it's in truly pristine condition inside and out. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and honestly, you won\u2019t find another one this spotless. It's been my pride and joy, but it's time for a new home. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
