      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been pampered every single mile. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have!",
