      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed, including a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with no signs of oxidative stress, while the factory suspension geometry provides the telepathic handling the platform is known for. A mechanically flawless specimen for the serious collector.",
